  3. Break Tasks Into Smaller Pieces

  Instead of:
  "Fix the Month view: week numbers, column width, delete icon, cancel button"

  Do:
  Task 1: "Move week numbers outside grid"
  Task 2: "Make columns wider"
  Task 3: "Add delete icon"
  Task 4: "Add cancel button"

  Each small task = less context = lower cost

